The buttery-caramel deliciousness of toffee meets chocolate in this decadent dip mix! Dip in with apple slices! Spread on brownies or dip it with your favorite sweet cracker or cookie for a sweet treat thatâ€™s perfect for any sweet tooth!

Ranch lovers. . . this is a delicious twist on your soon to be favorite dip mix. A truly unique pairing of savory avocado and a slightly peppery ranch. Perfect served with tortilla chips, fresh vegetables, potato chips or pretzels. Use as a zesty, creamy topping for nachos, tacos or quesadillas.

It doesn't get much better than this all time favorite combination! Dark chocolate cookie pieces combined with a vanilla sweet cream. Perfect served with fresh fruit, vanilla cookies, pretzel sticks (think sweet and salty) or on toasted bagels. Great recipe variation for a dessert cheeseball.

Yes, you got it right! We have taken an all American favorite warm chocolate drink and turned it into a cool, decadent dip mix. We even included the marshmallows! Perfect for year round enjoyment. Serve this sweet chocolatey dip mix with fresh fruits, cookies, pretzels or serve it as a topping on a vanilla or chocolate cake.

You say potato, I say potato. . .we may not agree on the pronunciation, but we can all agree this Loaded Baked Potato Dip is a hit! This mix is loaded with everything you love on a baked potato; chives, green onions, bacon, cheese, and sour cream (and even freeze dried potatoes). Serve this mix with potato chips, pita chips, pretzels, fresh vegetables or a neutral cracker.
Creamy white queso with the perfect pepper blend. This Queso Blanco Dip Mix is mild and delicious and will accompany your favorite tortilla chip perfectly!

column1: Mini Southern Style Cajun Dip Mix
column4:
A rich cajun flavor with a spicy flare! It's loaded with sun-dried tomatoes, celery, and spice. Makes several batches.  
Vegan
Contains: Soy & Wheat
(available in a mini size)

Sure to become your new favorite quick bread mix. A flavor explosion of your favorite savory flavors of onion and garlic along with sesame seeds, poppy seeds and salt. Delicious served with soups, casseroles and salads. Great sliced and toasted, served with butter and cream cheese. Be sure to have this on hand in your kitchen as an easy, perfect complement to your family's meals.

column1: No Bake Lemon Raspberry Cheesecake Mix
column4: This perfectly balanced no bake cheesecake combines fresh tart lemons and ripe raspberries to create a dessert that will hit the spot!

Make some delicious spiced apple cider with our Mulled Cider Spice! Makes up to 2 gallons of your favorite spiced cider (comes in a reusable pouch so that you can flavor a gallon at a time). Put the cider in a slow cooker and mix in for a warm party favorite! This product contains
No MSG
